twoSetSkill.name: Origin of Shields 2 Pieces
twoSetSkill.description: Gains a shield upon entry. The shield disappears upon taking an enemy hit and inflicts a 3s paralysis on nearby enemies. Shield appears again after 10s. When the shield is active, character gains 20% Lightning DMG.

threeSetSkill.name: Wings of Life 3 Pieces
threeSetSkill.description: Gain 20% Lightning DMG and 20% faster Move Speed. The shield of the Origin of Shields disappears after taking 2 hits.
